function App() {
	const [cumulativeData, setCumulativeData] = useState(CumulativeData);
	const handleAddGrades = (newCumulative) => {
		setCumulativeData([...cumulativeData, newCumulative]);
	};
	console.log(cumulativeData);
	return (
		<Router>
			<Container>
				<Row>
					<MyNavbar />
				</Row>
				<Routes>
					<Route exact path="/" element={<StudentTable />} />
					<Route path="/grade-criteria" element={<GradeCriteria />} />
					<Route
						path="/cumulative-sheet"
						element={
							<CumulativeTable
								cumulativeData={cumulativeData}
								addGrades={handleAddGrades}
							/>
						}
					/>
					<Route
						path="/finalized-grades"
						element={<FinalizedGradeList cumulativeData={cumulativeData} />}
					/>
				</Routes>
			</Container>
		</Router>
	);
}

export default App;
